0. db update
1. Pick number of players
2. One by one (formation picking) (until everyone picked a formation):
    1. Random formations sampled from formation pool
    2. Player picks a formation from given random samples
3. One by one (Athlete picking) (until all positions are filled):
    1. Player chooses which position to pick an athlete for
    2. Random athletes sampled from athlete pool
    3. Player picks an athlete from given random samples